With just a few weeks away from Spring. Cotton On is ready to release its Spring/Summer collection. Inspired by the Spring blossom, this collection has some floral, bright sweet colours and of course, denim. Whether you’re having a picnic at a park or finding the first crocuses and snowdrops, Cotton On this spring has the staple pieces you need for all your outdoor activities. Denim will forever be in style, every season. Picture: Supplied. The denim collection derives from the idea that denim is everyone’s favourite. Denims  are the key staple pieces you need to own in your wardrobe, they have the power to make you the coolest person in the room. Denim makes you look cool. Picture: Supplied. The Spring/Summer collection will be available at the end of this month.